long_desc.thetext:
Your package rtkit failed to build from source in current rawhide.
https://koji.fedoraproject.org/koji/taskinfo?taskID=17789502
For details on mass rebuild see https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Fedora_26_Mass_Rebuild
Is this package still useful? I see you deleted the upstream repo.
This bug appears to have been reported against 'rawhide' during the Fedora 26 development cycle. Changing version to '26'.
After an offline discussion with Lennart, the conclusion is that we'll leave things as they are for now.
FTR, correct upstream URL is http://git.0pointer.net/rtkit.git/ .
